Let's look at why it's so relevant.

00:03:03.780 --> 00:03:07.470
First, for banking, operations
and compliance, you need to

00:03:07.470 --> 00:03:11.370
follow RBI guidelines for
every single daily activity.

00:03:11.850 --> 00:03:16.980
For risk management, you must identify
and handle financial risks according

00:03:16.980 --> 00:03:19.260
to the frameworks these regulators set.

00:03:19.859 --> 00:03:23.850
